{"tid":2132387,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國警告巴西 採用華為5G設備將後果自負","createTime":"2020-07-30T10:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T04:27:49.000Z","uid":75656,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1386b1fb3af2adfbcc170b387eeaa6f7b439481a","tid":2132387,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:55:02.000Z","msg":"美國積極動員各國將華為排除在全球的5G項目，外媒報道，美國駐巴西大使查普曼(Todd Chapman)表示，如果巴西允許華為的5G技術在當地使用，將要「後果自負」。<br />\n<br />\n查普曼說，巴西若選用華為，中國政府隨時可以要求華為向其提供訊息，會構成國家安全的問題。他又指出，選用華為的後果可能來自經濟方面，美國最大的出口是知識產權，所以必須保護它。<br />\n<br />\n查普曼稱，美國的立場是向如巴西般的盟友發出預警，對於那些選擇和可靠的供應商購買產品的國家，美國準備通過美國國國際發展融資公司(IDFC)為5G建設項目提供資金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.now.com/news/post.php?id=600124\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.now.com%2Fnews%2Fpost.php%3Fid%3D600124&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSonGVh3W70%2FpCcVRRx8QUyg%3D&h=7d7be7af\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.now.com/news/post.php?id=600124</a>"},{"pid":"40d4da4a6705288b6c0a90d51fd63a04d344bbda","tid":2132387,"uid":273791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:55:22.000Z","msg":"奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62ecf8c026e7d3adcb03c7a6a90bd5b968d20a7","tid":2132387,"uid":279981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:56:08.000Z","msg":"肥西不是嚇大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060258e8fb8726dd19f629c5e12741ea6058cced","tid":2132387,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T11:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2028b31296df5759d2dc1a